ustify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,3783,200,IMG_5240.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,3783,200,IMG_5271.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span>